#. type: Title ##
#: ../src/guide/security/best-practices.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Basic principles"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/security/best-practices.md
msgid ""
"There are two main principles when it comes to security no matter which "
"application is being developed:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
#: ../src/guide/security/best-practices.md
msgid "Filter input."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '2. '
#: ../src/guide/security/best-practices.md
